data.description: Home is priced below market value.  List price is starting bid price. See attached EZ addendum.  This is a 1 level, 3 bedroom, 2 bath pool home.  It sits on a large corner lot with nice landscaping.  The open floor plan includes vaulted ceilings, plantation shutters and a spacious kitchen with stainless steal appliances, tile back splash, large upgraded sink and walk-in pantry.  The main bedroom has a walk-in closet, with bathroom with a walk-in shower, garden tub and linen closet.  Newer roof (2022), newer AC & hot water heater.  The windows have been upgraded to hurricane impact resistant windows.  The lanai is an oasis of relaxation with a heated pool, covered area and screened.  Just minutes from I-75 in a convenient location to shopping and restaurants.
